extends layout

block content
  #wrap
    .container
        img(class="bubble-background", src="images/static_bubbles.png")
        .row
            .col-md-5
                .text-background
                    .text-block
                        h2 #{title}.
                        p 
                        | I work as a software engineer at 
                        a(href="http://www.advent.com/", target="_blank") Advent Software
                        | . Advent has a 30 year history of delivering portfolio accounting software to more than 4,500 investment managers around the world.
                        p 
                        | At Advent, I spent six years working on 
                        a(href="http://www.advent.com/solutions/products/advent-revenue-center", target="_blank") Advent Revenue Center
                        | , an invoicing and revenue management application. Our clients used Revenue Center to automate complex portfolio billing calculations and other processes.
                        p
                        | I'm currently leading the development of an internal operations portal that monitors server and application software logs across customer implementations.
                        p
                        | I'm interested in building web applications that enable businesses to quickly understand complex business problems.  I especially like creating charts with the 
                        a(href="http://d3js.org/", target="_blank") D3.js 
                        | JavaScript library.
                        h3 Website
                        p
                        | The circles on the main page were created using D3.js's 
                        a(href="https://github.com/mbostock/d3/wiki/Force-Layout", target="_blank") Force Layout
                        | .
                        p
                        | This website was created using 
                        a(href="https://nodejs.org/", target="blank") Node.js
                        | , 
                        a(href="http://jade-lang.com/", target="blank") Jade 
                        | templating engine and 
                        a(href="http://learnboost.github.io/stylus/", target="blank") Stylus 
                        | css preprocessor. It uses a webhook to automatically deploy after each check-in.  Take a look at the 
                        a(href="https://github.com/sethisernhagen/node_personal", target="_blank") repository 
                        | on GitHub.
    #push
  .footer
      p
      | &copy; #{year} - Seth Isernhagen


